14382","2019-03-25T14:38:31.653Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1086345/answer","Biography information for Lord Agnew of Oulton","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1086345/answer",,,,,"60","Education","Education","2019-03-11","Children's Centres: Closures","2","House of Lords","To ask Her Majesty's Government how many Sure Start centres have closed in England since 2010.","false","Biography information for Lord Hain",,"Lord Hain","HL14383"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1086346","Department for Digital, Culture, Media and Sport","false","2019-03-19","<p>The Department for Digital, Culture, Media and Sport monitors proposed changes to library service provision throughout England, but does not hold complete figures on the number of public libraries closed since 2010.</p>",,"Lord Ashton of Hyde","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1086346/answer",,,,,,"2019-03-19T15:26:55.17Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1086346/answer","Biography information for Lord Ashton of Hyde","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1086346/answer",,,,,"10","Digital, Culture, Media and Sport","Digital, Culture, Media and Sport","2019-03-11","Public Libraries: Closures","2","House of Lords","To ask Her Majesty's Government how many libraries have closed in England since 2010.","false","Biography information for Lord Hain",,"Lord Hain","HL14384"
